{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-wiki-post-js","path":"/HOF_Framework/Form Customisations/basic-form-customisation","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#adding-steps\">Adding Steps</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#adding-fields\">Adding Fields</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#configuring-fields\">Configuring Fields</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#validation-rules\">Validation Rules</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#field-types\">Field Types</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#formatter\">Formatter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#field-labels\">Field Labels</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p>Now we have a basic form created then the next job is to add some steps and fields to our new form.</p>\n<p>In the directory we just created we should now find a directory <code class=\"language-jstext\">./apps/my-hof-form</code>. This contains the configuration and code for our app.</p>\n<p>Its contents should look something like this:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jstext line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jstext\">apps/my-hof-form/\n├── fields/\n├── translations/\n└── index.js</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"adding-steps\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#adding-steps\" aria-label=\"adding steps permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Adding Steps</h2>\n<p>Open the index.js file in a text editor. You will see a steps configuration that looks like this:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container govuk-visually-hidden\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"64351321252993850000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`steps: {\n  '/name': {\n    fields: ['name'],\n    next: '/confirm'\n  },\n  '/confirm': {\n    behaviours: ['complete', require('hof-behaviour-summary-page')],\n    next: '/complete'\n  },\n  '/complete': {}\n}`, `64351321252993850000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                Copy ›<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">example-steps.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsjs\"><span class=\"token literal-property property\">steps</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'/name'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">fields</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">next</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/confirm'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'/confirm'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">behaviours</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'complete'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'hof-behaviour-summary-page'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">next</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/complete'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'/complete'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>This defines the steps that our form takes, and the fields which are displayed on those steps.</p>\n<p>The keys of the <code class=\"language-jstext\">steps</code> object define the urls for each step.</p>\n<p>The basic configuration options you need to add a step can be seen on the <code class=\"language-jstext\">/name</code> step. The <code class=\"language-jstext\">fields</code> option defines which fields will be displayed, and the <code class=\"language-jstext\">next</code> option defines the step to which the user is taken when they complete the step.</p>\n<p>To add a new step between <code class=\"language-jstext\">/name</code> and <code class=\"language-jstext\">/confirm</code> to collect a user's address we add a child object with a key of <code class=\"language-jstext\">/address</code> to the steps object.</p>\n<p>Since it is going between <code class=\"language-jstext\">/name</code> and <code class=\"language-jstext\">/confirm</code> it should have a <code class=\"language-jstext\">next</code> property of <code class=\"language-jstext\">/confirm</code>, and we should modify the <code class=\"language-jstext\">next</code> property of the <code class=\"language-jstext\">/name</code> step to <code class=\"language-jstext\">/address</code>.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container govuk-visually-hidden\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"72512141605423250000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`steps: {\n  '/name': {\n    fields: ['name'],\n    next: '/address'\n  },\n  '/address': {\n    next: '/confirm'\n    },\n  '/confirm': {\n  ...`, `72512141605423250000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                Copy ›<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">add-new-step.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsjs\"><span class=\"token literal-property property\">steps</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'/name'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">fields</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">next</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/address'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'/address'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">next</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/confirm'</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'/confirm'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>Now if you restart your server (<code class=\"language-jstext\">Ctrl+C</code> to stop, then run the same command again) and go back to your form in the browser you will see that when you complete the <code class=\"language-jstext\">/name</code> step you are taken to <code class=\"language-jstext\">/address</code>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"adding-fields\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#adding-fields\" aria-label=\"adding fields permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Adding Fields</h2>\n<p>Now we need to add some fields to our new address step. This is as simple as adding the keys for those fields to the <code class=\"language-jstext\">fields</code> property of our new step object.</p>\n<p>We'll add five fields to this step to collect a full address.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container govuk-visually-hidden\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"48674659502220270000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`steps: {\n  ...\n  '/address': {\n    fields: ['address-line-1', 'address-line-2', 'town', 'country', 'postcode'],\n    next: '/confirm'\n  },\n  ...\n}`, `48674659502220270000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                Copy ›<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">add-field-to-steps.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsjs\"><span class=\"token literal-property property\">steps</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'/address'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">fields</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'address-line-1'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'address-line-2'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'town'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'country'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'postcode'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">next</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/confirm'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>Returning to the app in a browser and refreshing (you will need to restart your server each time you make changes - you can have this happen automatically when running locally by running <code class=\"language-jstext\">npm run start:dev</code> to start your server, which is recommended when you're developing an app) you will now see these fields on the address page.</p>\n<h3 id=\"configuring-fields\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#configuring-fields\" aria-label=\"configuring fields permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Configuring Fields</h3>\n<h4 id=\"validation-rules\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#validation-rules\" aria-label=\"validation rules permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Validation Rules</h4>\n<p>The next job is to configure the validation rules for our new fields. The configuration for this can be found in <code class=\"language-jstext\">./fields/index.js</code> in our app directory.</p>\n<p>You will see existing configuration for the <code class=\"language-jstext\">name</code> field that's already in our app. We can add new config objects for each of our new fields to this.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container govuk-visually-hidden\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"7796464432611172000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`module.exports = {\n  name: {\n    validate: 'required'\n  },\n  'address-line-1': {},\n  'address-line-2': {},\n  town: {},\n  country: {},\n  postcode: {}\n};`, `7796464432611172000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                Copy ›<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">field-validations.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsjs\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">validate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'required'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'address-line-1'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'address-line-2'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">town</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">country</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">postcode</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>We want to make all of the fields except <code class=\"language-jstext\">address-line-2</code> mandatory, and so can give them a <code class=\"language-jstext\">validate</code> property of <code class=\"language-jstext\">'required'</code>.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container govuk-visually-hidden\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"64862677891916060000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`module.exports = {\n  name: {\n    validate: 'required'\n  },\n  'address-line-1': {\n    validate: 'required'\n  },\n  'address-line-2': {},\n  town: {\n    validate: 'required'\n  },\n  country: {\n    validate: 'required'\n  },\n  postcode: {\n    validate: 'required'\n  }\n};`, `64862677891916060000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                Copy ›<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">required-validations.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsjs\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">validate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'required'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'address-line-1'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">validate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'required'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'address-line-2'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">town</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">validate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'required'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">country</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">validate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'required'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">postcode</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">validate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'required'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>Additionally, we might want to do validation on the postcode to make sure it is correctly formatted, and so we can add an additional <code class=\"language-jstext\">postcode</code> validator. To add multiple validators to a field, simply set the validate property to an array.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container govuk-visually-hidden\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"90831057610610570000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`postcode: {\n  validate: ['required', 'postcode']\n}`, `90831057610610570000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                Copy ›<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">multiple-validations.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsjs\"><span class=\"token literal-property property\">postcode</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">validate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'required'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'postcode'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/UKHomeOfficeForms/hof-form-controller/blob/master/lib/validation/validators.js\">full list of built-in validation types</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"field-types\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#field-types\" aria-label=\"field types permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Field Types</h4>\n<p>By default all fields are <code class=\"language-jstext\">input[type=text]</code> unless otherwise specified. In this case, we possibly want our country field to be a <code class=\"language-jstext\">select</code> element instead.</p>\n<p>To do this we add a <code class=\"language-jstext\">mixin</code> property of <code class=\"language-jstext\">select</code> to that field.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container govuk-visually-hidden\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"71475922709441610000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`country: {\n  mixin: 'select',\n  validate: 'required'\n}`, `71475922709441610000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                Copy ›<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">field-mixins.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsjs\"><span class=\"token literal-property property\">country</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">mixin</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'select'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">validate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'required'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>We also need to add some options for the field. Fortunately there is a Home Office managed list of countries, so we don't need to handle this ourselves. Install <code class=\"language-jstext\">hof-util-countries</code> from npm, and then add the following:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container govuk-visually-hidden\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"96510680458673210000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`country: {\n  mixin: 'select',\n  options: require('hof-util-countries')(),\n  validate: 'required'\n}`, `96510680458673210000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                Copy ›<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">field-options.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsjs\"><span class=\"token literal-property property\">country</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">mixin</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'select'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">options</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'hof-util-countries'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">validate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'required'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>For more <code class=\"language-jstext\">mixin</code> options and field configuration settings see <a href=\"https://npmjs.com/hof-template-mixins\">hof-template-mixins</a>.</p>\n<h4 id=\"formatter\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#formatter\" aria-label=\"formatter permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Formatter</h4>\n<p>Some text inputs will include characters you don't wish to be recorded (e.g. hyphens or spaces). To remove these with the <code class=\"language-jstext\">formatter field</code>.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container govuk-visually-hidden\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"74608278231641780000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`sortCode: {\n  mixin: 'textarea'\n  validate: 'required',\n  formatter: ['removehyphens']\n}`, `74608278231641780000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                Copy ›<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">field-formatters.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsjs\"><span class=\"token literal-property property\">sortCode</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">mixin</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'textarea'</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">validate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'required'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">formatter</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'removehyphens'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>You can also use the formatter field to ensure the characters recorded are all in upper or lower case.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container govuk-visually-hidden\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"81213623565866630000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`brpNumber: {\n  mixin: 'textarea'\n  validate: 'required',\n  formatter: ['uppercase']\n}`, `81213623565866630000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                Copy ›<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">uppercase-formatter.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsjs\"><span class=\"token literal-property property\">brpNumber</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">mixin</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'textarea'</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">validate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'required'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">formatter</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'uppercase'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>For other <code class=\"language-jstext\">formatting</code> options see <a href=\"https://github.com/UKHomeOfficeForms/hof-form-controller/blob/master/lib/formatting/formatters.js\">hof-controller-formatters</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"field-labels\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#field-labels\" aria-label=\"field labels permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Field Labels</h4>\n<p>The last thing to do is to add some label content for our new fields. You will see that right now they appear with default labels like <code class=\"language-jstext\">fields.address-line-1.label</code>.</p>\n<p>To add label content for our new fields we need to set some properties in <code class=\"language-jstext\">./translations/src/en/fields.json</code>. You will see here that there is a label defined for the name field. We can add some more labels for our new fields as follows:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container govuk-visually-hidden\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"98574215793416400000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`{\n  &quot;name&quot;: {\n    &quot;label&quot;: &quot;Name&quot;\n  },\n  &quot;address-line-1&quot;: {\n    &quot;label&quot;: &quot;Address&quot;\n  },\n  &quot;address-line-2&quot;: {\n    &quot;label&quot;: &quot;Address line 2&quot;\n  },\n  &quot;town&quot;: {\n    &quot;label&quot;: &quot;Town&quot;\n  },\n  &quot;country&quot;: {\n    &quot;label&quot;: &quot;Country&quot;\n  },\n  &quot;postcode&quot;: {\n    &quot;label&quot;: &quot;Postcode&quot;\n  }\n}`, `98574215793416400000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                Copy ›<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">fields.json</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-jsjson line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-jsjson\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"label\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Name\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"address-line-1\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"label\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Address\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"address-line-2\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"label\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Address line 2\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"town\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"label\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Town\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"country\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"label\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Country\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"postcode\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"label\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Postcode\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>Returning to your app in a browser you will now see that the new address fields now use the labels we defined for them.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"#fields\">more information about how the content for fields can be configured</a></p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"path":null,"title":"Basic Form Customisation","tags":null}}},"pageContext":{"title":"Basic Form Customisation","slug":"/HOF_Framework/Form Customisations/basic-form-customisation/","tags":null,"breadcrumb":{"location":"/HOF_Framework/Form Customisations/basic-form-customisation","crumbs":[{"pathname":"/","crumbLabel":"Home"},{"pathname":"/HOF_Framework","crumbLabel":"HOF_Framework"},{"pathname":"/HOF_Framework/Form Customisations","crumbLabel":"Form Customisations"},{"pathname":"/HOF_Framework/Form Customisations/basic-form-customisation","crumbLabel":"basic-form-customisation"}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2744294623","3649515864","3684199878"]}